standalone.com.sun.source.tree.TreeVisitor<Void,​standalone.com.sun.source.util.Trees>
public class Java2TypeScriptTranslator extends AbstractTreePrinter
This is a TypeScript printer for translating the Java AST to a TypeScript program.
Author:
Renaud Pawlak, Louis Grignon

    • Java2TypeScriptTranslator

      public Java2TypeScriptTranslator​(PrinterAdapter adapter, TranspilationHandler logHandler, JSweetContext context, standalone.com.sun.source.tree.CompilationUnitTree compilationUnit, boolean fillSourceMap)
      Creates a new TypeScript translator.
      Parameters:
      adapter - an object that can tune various aspects of the TypeScript code generation
      logHandler - the handler for logging and error reporting
      context - the AST scanning context
      compilationUnit - the compilation unit to be translated
      fillSourceMap - if true, the printer generates the source maps, for debugging purpose
